			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>July 9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1866</date></p>
				<p>Revd <del>Mr</del> <addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p rend="Note&#58;"> Revd is written over Mr</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><placeName>Phila</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">I beg to trespass<lb/> on your valuable time so much as to<lb/> ask if you would procure a circular<lb/> of the best Catholic Orphan Institution<lb/> in your city or vicinity&#44; where a <add>female</add> orphan can<lb/> be thoroughly educated &#38; be trained to some<lb/> kind of occupation&#44; so that at the proper age<lb/> it will be <sic>independant</sic> of the world &#38; able<lb/> to earn its own livehood&#8212;I am induced<lb/> to make this inquiry for a friend living in <placeName>Va<add>&#63;</add></placeName><lb/> who is willing to pay any small or reason<hi rend="underline">a</hi><lb/>ble amt towards the proper education of this<lb/> child &#38; I will esteem it a great favor if you<lb/> would give me such information as I require&#44;<lb/> which from your long acquaintance with the char<hi rend="underline">i</hi><lb/>table institutions of your city&#44; I imagine you can<lb/> do readily.  Hoping you are in improved health<lb/> &#38; with renewed assurances of esteem &#38; an<lb/> apology for thus<add>&#63;</add> intruding on your time I am</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">Yours very Truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">M. M. Davis</persName>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><placeName>Box 2524 N. Y. P. O.</placeName></p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p rend="align(center)">Notre dame</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">Ready Har<add>&#63;</add></p>
				<p rend="align(center)indent(1)">Mid</p>
				<p rend="align(center)indent(-1)"><persName>J. M Sevill</persName> <placeName>19 South Na<add>&#63;</add></placeName></p>
